snippet.title: Sega Pico Game: Bishoujo Senshi Sailor Moon Sailor Stars - Tokimeki Party (1996 Bandai)
snippet.description:
Bishoujo Senshi Sailor Moon Sailor Stars: Tokimeki Party (美少女戦士セーラームーン セーラースターズ ときめきパーティ) is a Sega Pico game based upon the Sailor Moon Sailor Stars anime series.
